-*--------------------------------------+--------------------------------------+
-| WebAppProxy                          | YARN_PROXYSERVER_HEAPSIZE            |
-*--------------------------------------+--------------------------------------+
-| Map Reduce Job History Server        | HADOOP_JOB_HISTORYSERVER_HEAPSIZE    |
-*--------------------------------------+--------------------------------------+
